    <item>
      <title>美国因以色列袭击扩大对伊朗石油行业的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/us-sanctions-iran-linked-ships-and-companies-over-israel-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为对伊朗发射弹道导弹袭击以色列的回应，美国扩大了对伊朗石油和天然气行业的制裁范围，在以色列可能采取报复行动之前加大对伊朗的经济压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/us-sanctions-iran-linked-ships-and-companies-over-israel-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 18:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲安全峰会前夕，巴基斯坦枪手杀害 20 名矿工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-11/urgent-gunmen-kill-20-miners-and-wound-others-in-an-attack-in-southwest-pakistan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦奎达（美联社） — 一名警方官员周五称，枪手在巴基斯坦西南部杀死了 21 名矿工，造成 6 人受伤，当局对此予以谴责，并已开始搜寻袭击者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-11/urgent-gunmen-kill-20-miners-and-wound-others-in-an-attack-in-southwest-pakistan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 02:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
